						               													<description>From the back cover:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The bloodthirsty spectators of the gladiatorial arena would shout out &amp;quot;Habet, hoc habet!&amp;quot; whenever a gladiator fell in combat.  Now you can recreate those violent contests with the latest miniature wargaming rules from Flagship Games.  Habet, Hoc Habet! includes:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Rules for recreating gladiator combat, where the actions of the individual determine all!&amp;#10;     A campaign system where you play the gladiators' owner, training them for their bloody task, and sending them to their fate on the sands of the arena!&amp;#10;     All the weapons used by the gladiators of ancient times!&amp;#10;     Chariot races!&amp;#10;     Hours of enjoyment for you and your gaming buddies!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Habet, Hoc Habet! faithfully recreates the life of the gladiator and the gladiator's owner, the Lanista, as the later strives to make his fortune while the former does his best to stay alive!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Habet, Hoc Habet! is a great game for two players or a whole club.  You can play out an entire campaign in the course of an evening, and no more than a single figure per person is needed!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Make a claim for glory.  Play Habet, Hoc Habet!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;BONUS FEATURE: Fantasy Gladiator Rules!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Home Page: http://www.flagshipgames.com/html/habet__hoc_habet_.html&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
